H0.text: An anteater is an example of an annelid.

H1.text: A honey bee is an example of an annelid.

H2.text: A sea star is an example of an annelid.

H3.text: An earthworm is an example of an annelid.

A4.text: An earthworm is a soil-dwelling terrestrial invertebrate that belongs to the phylum Annelida.
